    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "The Eth Beacon Node API technically allows to return `400` for `Invalid state or validator ID, or status`, so I think the other clients must comply to this behavior.\r\n\r\nA fix by Teku side is however about the content of the response: `\"status\":400` should be changed in `\"code\":400`.\r\n\r\nSo, currently no client is compliant with the specs :smile: ",
