    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Did a little testing.\nvalidator id of `-1` throws a 400, much the same as the invalid pubkey above, where as a pubkey thats valid and not found will just not be added to the list, so i think the behaviour is consistent with that.\nI've raised a spec issue on the api and will see if there's a lot of discussion there about it. I think that now that we've fixed the response it's probably ok as it stands, but it's just a matter of if there's traction on clarifying the standard api to describe 'invalid id' ",
